                          font-family: Noto Sans SC, Arial, sans-serif;
                          font-size: 16px;
                          font-weight: 700;
                          letter-spacing: 0;
                          line-height: 23px;
                          text-align: center;
                          color: #020e36;
                        ">
                            Здравейте, ${fullName}
